{
  "chapter": 25,
  "chapter_summary": "乌卓秘密来访，告知项少龙魏王暗中支持灰胡马贼袭击车队，且魏王与信陵君存在权力斗争。项少龙获一百名好手相助。小昭等八女为项少龙缝制飞针束腰内甲。项少龙误将赵倩当作赵雅冒犯，赵倩含羞逃走。雅夫人因此与项少龙激烈争吵，怒叱他不可惹赵倩。赵大告密少原君进入雅夫人寝室，项少龙闯入撞破二人搂抱，与雅夫人彻底决裂，宣布恩尽义绝。雅夫人哀求解释遭拒。项少龙夜练飞针攀爬工具，潜入平原夫人院落偷听，得知惊人阴谋：信陵君策划让项少龙行刺魏王，成功后灭口嫁祸赵人，以此夺取魏国军权。平原夫人更计划破赵倩处子之躯，胁迫项少龙就范。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_cheng_xu",
      "speaker_name": "成胥",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "乌家有人来找你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 2,
      "line_end": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_zhuo",
      "speaker_name": "乌卓",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "乌卓拜见孙姑爷。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_zhuo",
      "speaker_name": "乌卓",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "我们奉主人之命，为孙姑爷做先头部队探路，果然有收获。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_zhuo",
      "speaker_name": "乌卓",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "不知是谁放出消息，魏、赵境内几股最凶悍的马贼，已经晓得孙姑爷你护送珍宝和赵国最动人的美女前赴大梁，形势对孙姑爷非常不利。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_wu_zhuo",
      "text": "魏人不会坐视不理吧？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_zhuo",
      "speaker_name": "乌卓",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "魏国有人向我们暗通消息，安厘王不但不会派人保护你们，还供应马匹、兵器给其中最大一股叫灰胡的马贼，暗遣他们攻击你们的车马队。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_wu_zhuo",
      "text": "灰胡不是曾经在赵国境内偷袭我们的马贼吗？为何会在魏境出现？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_zhuo",
      "speaker_name": "乌卓",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "正是此人，当日他们偷袭不成，损兵折将，事后被赵人围剿，所以逃入魏境，沿途招纳乱民，现在人数增达千人以上，不可小觑。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_zhuo",
      "speaker_name": "乌卓",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "一直以来，我们怀疑赵境内的几股马贼，都有魏王在背后支持，好削弱赵国国力，所以他们每遇形势危急时，都会逃进魏境避难，现在更证实了这个想法。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_wu_zhuo",
      "text": "可是我们今天是要把赵国的三公主送给魏人，为何魏王用这种手段招待我们呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_zhuo",
      "speaker_name": "乌卓",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "真正的原因我也弄不清楚，不过可猜想这定牵涉到魏王与信陵君间的权力斗争。自信陵君盗兵符大败秦兵后，功高震主，当然会惹起魏王的疑忌。况且信陵君曾长留邯郸，若魏王能破坏这次婚约，受打击最大的当然是信陵君和赵人的关系。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_zhuo",
      "speaker_name": "乌卓",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "而这次婚约，乃信陵君一手促成的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_zhuo",
      "speaker_name": "乌卓",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "灰胡里有我们的卧底，据知灰胡对你恨之入骨，决意要把你和所有女眷生擒，再当你面前淫辱诸女，以泄心头之恨。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_wu_zhuo",
      "text": "这只是他的痴心妄想。有没有那不想做人，只想做禽兽的嚣魏牟的消息？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_zhuo",
      "speaker_name": "乌卓",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "这人向以神出鬼没著名，每次攻击都是突然出现，教人抓不到半点先兆，比灰胡可怕多了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "今天到魏的路线，早由赵穆亲自定下来，又得赵王同意，不能更改。假若泄秘者是赵穆，那等于敌人对我们的路程了如指掌，我们岂非完全处于被动的劣势？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_zhuo",
      "speaker_name": "乌卓",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "孙姑爷怎会是盲从听命的人？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_wu_zhuo",
      "text": "你真知我心意。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_zhuo",
      "speaker_name": "乌卓",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "今天小人带来一百名好手，充当孙姑爷的家将，嘿！能在孙姑爷手下办事，我们都非常兴奋。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cheng_xu",
      "speaker_name": "成胥",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "我立即找查元裕商量一下，要他多带粮草并添加装备，好应付贼子的进攻。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_qian",
      "speaker_name": "赵倩",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "少龙！你对赵倩干了什么好事？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ya_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "雅夫人",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "给我站着！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_ya_fu_ren",
      "text": "夫人有什么吩咐？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ya_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "雅夫人",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "你难道不知道绝不可以惹赵倩吗？",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_ya_fu_ren",
      "text": "卑职以后不敢，可以告退了吗？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ya_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "雅夫人",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "好！项少龙，给我立即滚出去！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_da",
      "speaker_name": "赵大",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "项爷为我们三兄弟作主，少原君那奸贼来找夫人，密谈两句后，夫人便把他请入寝室内去了。",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_da",
      "text": "你当作从未来过我这里，知道吗？",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_da",
      "speaker_name": "赵大",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "我什么都不怕。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "让开！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_yuan_jun",
      "speaker_name": "少原君",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "好大胆！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 189
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ya_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "雅夫人",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "不要！",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_ya_fu_ren",
      "text": "尽管护着他吧！由今天开始，我再不管你的私事。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ya_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "雅夫人",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "是我不好，误会你了。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_ya_fu_ren",
      "text": "问过三公主了吗？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ya_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "雅夫人",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "为何你不向我解释？人家也会妒忌的嘛！",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_ya_fu_ren",
      "text": "这事现在无关痛痒，夜深了！夫人请回去歇息，明天还要趁早赶路。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ya_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "雅夫人",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "少龙！求你听我解释，是他要强吻我，我……",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_ya_fu_ren",
      "text": "若你能解释为何会邀请一个刚残杀了你的心腹手下，又是我项少龙的仇人，并且曾与你有染的好色狂徒到你房内，我便原谅你。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_ya_fu_ren",
      "text": "夫人！我已不计较你和赵穆联手害我的事，因为本人误以为你会从此一心一意跟从我。到今天才发觉只是我一厢情愿的想法。就算你要拣，也不应拣少原君！这里的精壮男儿少说有几百人，拣任何一个都会使我好受一点。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ya_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "雅夫人",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "你在侮辱我，我真的……",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_ya_fu_ren",
      "text": "闭嘴！这一掌代表我们间恩尽义绝，你欢喜跟谁也好，我再不管你。看我不顺眼的话，便请你王兄杀了我吧！不过莫怪我没有提醒你，谁想杀我害我，当要付出惨痛的代价。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ya_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "雅夫人",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "不！",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_yuan_jun",
      "speaker_name": "少原君",
      "listener": "char_ping_yuan_fu_ren",
      "text": "若非那项少龙闯进来，我定能把那淫妇治死。哼！看她还敢否不依我。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ping_yuan_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "平原夫人",
      "listener": "char_shao_yuan_jun",
      "text": "孩儿何需急在一时，赵雅迟早是你囊中之物，连赵倩亦逃不过你的五指关，哼！",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ping_yuan_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "平原夫人",
      "listener": "char_shao_yuan_jun",
      "text": "你不要再去惹项少龙，这人对你舅父有极大的利用价值。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 306
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_yuan_jun",
      "speaker_name": "少原君",
      "listener": "char_ping_yuan_fu_ren",
      "text": "他对孩儿如此恶劣，我怎忍得下这口气，除非娘清楚说出你会怎样对付他，否则我定要和他过不去。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 308
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_yuan_jun",
      "speaker_name": "少原君",
      "listener": "char_ping_yuan_fu_ren",
      "text": "娘啊！孩儿大了，应可以为你和舅父分担心事吧！",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 310,
      "line_end": 312
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ping_yuan_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "平原夫人",
      "listener": "char_shao_yuan_jun",
      "text": "你知否为何舅父会一力促成赵、魏两国间这场婚事，又故意把《鲁公秘录》的秘密泄露给赵人知道？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 316,
      "line_end": 318
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_yuan_jun",
      "speaker_name": "少原君",
      "listener": "char_ping_yuan_fu_ren",
      "text": "娘！快点说啊！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ping_yuan_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "平原夫人",
      "listener": "char_shao_yuan_jun",
      "text": "此乃天大秘密，除你我外，绝不可给第三个人知道，明白吗？",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 324,
      "line_end": 326
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ping_yuan_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "平原夫人",
      "listener": "char_shao_yuan_jun",
      "text": "我是不得不说给你知，因为尚要由你配合舅父派来的高手，进行这项重要的任务。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 330,
      "line_end": 332
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_yuan_jun",
      "speaker_name": "少原君",
      "listener": "char_ping_yuan_fu_ren",
      "text": "这个包在我身上。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 334,
      "line_end": 334
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ping_yuan_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "平原夫人",
      "listener": "char_shao_yuan_jun",
      "text": "赵人为偷取《鲁公秘录》，必然会派出他们最好的高手赴魏，现在他们派了项少龙，此人心计、剑术均非常了得，正合我们心意。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 336,
      "line_end": 338
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_yuan_jun",
      "speaker_name": "少原君",
      "listener": "char_ping_yuan_fu_ren",
      "text": "舅父想招纳他吗？可是他和孩儿……",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 340,
      "line_end": 341
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ping_yuan_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "平原夫人",
      "listener": "char_shao_yuan_jun",
      "text": "放心吧！你的敌人就是我的敌人，我会教他死无葬身之地。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 342,
      "line_end": 344
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_yuan_jun",
      "speaker_name": "少原君",
      "listener": "char_ping_yuan_fu_ren",
      "text": "好极了！",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 346,
      "line_end": 346
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ping_yuan_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "平原夫人",
      "listener": "char_shao_yuan_jun",
      "text": "只要收买这蠢蛋，我们可安排他行刺魏国那昏君，有你舅父的协助，兼之这傻瓜武功高强，定能成功。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 352,
      "line_end": 354
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_yuan_jun",
      "speaker_name": "少原君",
      "listener": "char_ping_yuan_fu_ren",
      "text": "什么？",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 356,
      "line_end": 356
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ping_yuan_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "平原夫人",
      "listener": "char_shao_yuan_jun",
      "text": "看你惊成那样子，只要项少龙得手，你舅父的人便会当场把他杀死，落个死无对证，然后把责任全推在赵人身上，那时你舅父便可名正言顺借口出兵讨伐赵人，把军权拿到手里，魏国还不是他囊中之物吗？",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 358,
      "line_end": 360
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_yuan_jun",
      "speaker_name": "少原君",
      "listener": "char_ping_yuan_fu_ren",
      "text": "果是天衣无缝的妙计，可是项少龙绝非愚笨之徒，最怕他阳奉阴违，向魏王告我们一状，那便糟透。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 362,
      "line_end": 364
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ping_yuan_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "平原夫人",
      "listener": "char_shao_yuan_jun",
      "text": "不要小看我和你舅父，当年娘嫁给你爹，就是希望他能坐上王位，岂知他不成大器，死得又早，否则你早成赵国之主。我们也想好了对付项少龙的方法，就是要逼得他走投无路，只好投靠我们。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 368,
      "line_end": 372
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ping_yuan_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "平原夫人",
      "listener": "char_shao_yuan_jun",
      "text": "只要能破掉赵倩的处子之躯，那时他还能到哪里去呢？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 378,
      "line_end": 380
    }
  ],
